The paper deals with wireless sensor networks, which are typically studied in the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The use of relay nodes and power allocation also suggests the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of computer simulations, which could fall under the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the optimization techniques used in the paper could also be relevant to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
